

This script installs the RPCore components over the KVM node :

1. It asks for the location of installation
2. Installs the RPCore components and libvirt
3. During installation, it also asks if the user needs to install nontpmrpcore.
4. If yes, it installs nontpmrpcore and also installs the necessary scripts in rc.local
5. Otherwise, it only updates rc.local with rp_listener
